        "text": "Addie was the photographer for my husband and I's wedding this August, and we could not have asked for a better photographer!!! From our first meeting to the final gallery, Addie was incredibly friendly, fun, warm, and talented. She not only took beautiful photos, but was an incredible support on wedding day. Thank you Addie for documenting all of the special moments on our wedding day; Noah and I are going to love looking back on the wonderful memories you captured!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-12",
        "text": "Addie is the absolute BEST!!!! Not only is she an amazing photographer, she is genuinely an incredible person! From our first conversation to the wedding day we knew we were in the best hands possible. Her talent, warm and bubbly personality, organization, caring nature and professionalism made her the perfect person to capture our story! On the day of the wedding, she was calm and somehow everywhere, never missing a moment but didn’t feel intrusive. The pictures are absolutely stunning!!! They are natural, capturing true emotions, and beautifully edited. We are beyond grateful to Addie for the priceless pictures and would 100% use her again and recommend her to anyone!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-07",
        "text": "Addie photographed our wedding. Not only were the final photos beyond anything I could’ve asked for, but she personally made our night so much fun. She’s professional, timely, quick to act in the moment and fantastic at directing guests and bridal parties to capture every moment. We had so much fun shooting with Addie and her photos turned out unbelievable. She is talented, experienced and hilarious! We will recommend her every chance we get. Thank you for giving us memories of our beautiful day Addie!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-11",
        "text": "Addie was AMAZING! We are absolutely OBSESSED with our photos. She went above and beyond! She flew from Colorado to Arizona for our engagement pictures and even helped us pick out outfits!\n\nOur pictures are absolutely breathtaking and she made it such a good experience! My fiancé had a blast and said it was like a fun little date. Couldn't have had a better time! She made us feel so comfortable."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-09",
        "text": "Addie was a last minute booked photographer because mine ended up being sick & couldn’t shoot. This was a destination wedding for us so I was nervous not knowing her at all. She was absolutely amazing. Addie went above & beyond our expectations! Very friendly & very easy to work with. She will make sure all your needs are met & naturally makes everything run smoothly. What started as a very stressful & chaotic situation (with our previous photographer not be able to come) turned out to be absolutely perfect with Addie! I’m so happy everything fell into place as it did. 😊"
